author: amaniatis
msg: This is a 2 colour t shirt design (for a dark coloured t-shirt). It includes a rendering of the feather in two colours
since that makes printing t-shirts cheaper and it looks better than CMYK. This feather is designed to reverse out of dark background.
This design was used for the Sydney barcamp in 2010. The Apache word was created in Interstate since I was unable to find
the official font for a use like this with an additional word "barcamp"
